OL,7,FA permanent resting place for those
OL,8,Faffected by the discovery of ashes at
OL,9,Fa Hull funeral directors has been
OL,10,Fconfirmed.
OL,12,FEast Riding of Yorkshire Council and
OL,13,FHull City Council have committed to
OL,14,Fdesigning a memorial for loved ones
OL,15,Finvolved by the ongoing Legacy Funeral
OL,16,Fscandal.
