OL,3,CPlans for a permanent memorial for
OL,4,Cthose affected by funeral directors
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FHumberside Police began looking into
OL,8,Fthe business on 6 March after a report
OL,9,Fof "concern for care of the deceased",
OL,10,Fprompting a string of concern from
OL,11,Fmore people.
OL,13,FIt led to the removal of 35 bodies and
OL,14,Fa quantity of ashes from the premises.
OL,16,FIn July, officers said 163 families
OL,17,Fhad been linked to the discovered
OL,18,Fashes at sites in Hessle Road and
OL,19,FAnlaby Road in Hull, and Beckside in
OL,20,FBeverley.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
