OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FThe council says the bereaved families
OL,8,Fwill be involved in the process
OL,9,Fthroughout.
OL,11,FHull City Council's director of adult
OL,12,Fsocial care, Tracy Meyerhoff, said:
OL,13,F"We recognise that it is important for
OL,14,Fpeople who have been affected by this
OL,15,Fvery upsetting situation to have a
OL,16,Fpermanent place where they can
OL,17,Fremember their loved ones in peace and
OL,18,Ftranquillity.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
