OL,3,CPlans for a permanent memorial for
OL,4,Cthose affected by funeral directors
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"We intend to create a place where
OL,8,Fpeople can feel close to their loved
OL,9,Fone's memory with dignity and where
OL,10,Four community can remember and
OL,11,Freflect."
OL,13,FThree people have since been arrested
OL,14,Fin connection with the investigation.
OL,16,FIn March, a 46-year-old man and a 23-
OL,17,Fyear-old woman were arrested on
OL,18,Fsuspicion of prevention of a lawful
OL,19,Fand decent burial, fraud by false
OL,20,Frepresentation and fraud by abuse of
OL,21,Fposition.
